      section.hero
        .container
          h1.title PiperNet Is Here
      section.problem
        .container
          h2.sub-title The Problem
          .problem-description
            p Beneath the flashy homepages of your favorite sites lurk Hooli and other evil corporations out to hoard and sell your most personal data.
            p What was built to be the ultimate platform for the free sharing of knowledge has turned into a money-gungry monster feasting on our privacy and freedom.
            p But fear not, for Pied Piper has the answer! And it's simple: An autonomous peer-to-peer network featuring distributed storage powered by universal compression, accelerated scheduling allocation, and end-to-end encryption.
            p Put even simpler - 
              span it's the internet, completely decentralized.
      section.banner
        .container
          .banner-description We're in this together! All of our computers and phones join in a network to make the strongest supercomputer the world has ever seen.
      section.introducing
        .container
          h2.sub-title Introducing PiedPiperCoin
          .pic-decoration
          span Pied Piper's new interner is built for users, by users.
          span You supply the storage, compute, and networking resources that power our entire decentralized web.
          p Now there's a way to give credit where credit is due. Compute credit, that is! The more you share your device resources, the more  PiedPiper Coin you receive.
          p Whether you're a developer with an app ready for market, or just an Average Joe with a smartphone you'll love all you can do with PiedPiperCoin.
